==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sisal hemp
<hw>Si*sal" hemp`</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>,}</mhw> <def>The prepared fiber of the <spn>Agave
Americana</spn>, or American aloe, used for cordage; -- so called from
<etsep>Sisal</etsep>, a port in Yucatan. See <cref>Sisal hemp</cref>,
under <er>Hemp</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Siscowet</ent>⟦br⟧
